From 0277b70999712586ebd4c3ebfb33fea35c691db2 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: SlayZone Dev <dev@slayzone.local>
Date: Sat, 18 Apr 2026 07:04:44 +0200
Subject: [1/7] slayzone: rebrand Chromium -> SlayZone (Phase 2.1 placeholder)

Placeholder text-only rebrand. Real icon / splash / about-page artwork
swapped in during Phase 19 distribution work (tracked on the parity
ledger). Everything user-visible that reads from IDS_PRODUCT_NAME or
the chrome/app/theme/chromium/BRANDING template picks up "SlayZone"
automatically.

- chrome/app/theme/chromium/BRANDING: COMPANY/PRODUCT/COPYRIGHT =>
  SlayZone. MAC_BUNDLE_ID zone.slay.SlayZone. MAC_CREATOR_CODE Slay.
  Installer strings follow.
- chrome/app/chromium_strings.grd: IDS_PRODUCT_NAME +
  IDS_SHORT_PRODUCT_NAME "Chromium" -> "SlayZone". Scoped to the
  is_chrome_for_testing_branded else-branch since our build sets
  is_chrome_branded = false.

Mac assets (app.icns, product_logo_*.png) remain the upstream
Chromium placeholder art; they read fine under a text-only rebrand
and are cheaper to swap once once real assets land than to regenerate
noise-matching stand-ins now.
---
 chrome/app/chromium_strings.grd    |  4 ++--
 chrome/app/theme/chromium/BRANDING | 18 +++++++++---------
 2 files changed, 11 insertions(+), 11 deletions(-)

diff --git a/chrome/app/chromium_strings.grd b/chrome/app/chromium_strings.grd
index 7ce756fd08a9d..35bfe9bb6f94d 100644
--- a/chrome/app/chromium_strings.grd
+++ b/chrome/app/chromium_strings.grd
@@ -294,10 +294,10 @@ If you update this file, be sure also to update google_chrome_strings.grd. -->
         </then>
         <else>
           <message name="IDS_PRODUCT_NAME" desc="The Chrome application name" translateable="false">
-            Chromium
+            SlayZone
           </message>
           <message name="IDS_SHORT_PRODUCT_NAME" desc="The Chrome application short name." translateable="false">
-            Chromium
+            SlayZone
           </message>
         </else>
       </if>
diff --git a/chrome/app/theme/chromium/BRANDING b/chrome/app/theme/chromium/BRANDING
index f8363d5b294fe..545b303c603d3 100644
--- a/chrome/app/theme/chromium/BRANDING
+++ b/chrome/app/theme/chromium/BRANDING
@@ -1,10 +1,10 @@
-COMPANY_FULLNAME=The Chromium Authors
-COMPANY_SHORTNAME=The Chromium Authors
-PRODUCT_FULLNAME=Chromium
-PRODUCT_SHORTNAME=Chromium
-PRODUCT_INSTALLER_FULLNAME=Chromium Installer
-PRODUCT_INSTALLER_SHORTNAME=Chromium Installer
-COPYRIGHT=Copyright @LASTCHANGE_YEAR@ The Chromium Authors. All rights reserved.
-MAC_BUNDLE_ID=org.chromium.Chromium
-MAC_CREATOR_CODE=Cr24
+COMPANY_FULLNAME=SlayZone
+COMPANY_SHORTNAME=SlayZone
+PRODUCT_FULLNAME=SlayZone
+PRODUCT_SHORTNAME=SlayZone
+PRODUCT_INSTALLER_FULLNAME=SlayZone Installer
+PRODUCT_INSTALLER_SHORTNAME=SlayZone Installer
+COPYRIGHT=Copyright @LASTCHANGE_YEAR@ SlayZone. All rights reserved.
+MAC_BUNDLE_ID=zone.slay.SlayZone
+MAC_CREATOR_CODE=Slay
 MAC_TEAM_ID=
